Week 1
Brief: 1
Scenario: Onboarding & Market Familiarization
Task:
Introduce yourself and your background,
        Set up marketing tools accounts (Google Analytics, Meta Business Suite, Canva, Wordpress, Elementor)
        Research and document 3 competitors in your field, their digital presence and summarize findings


Brief: 2
Scenario: Content Audit
Tasks: 
        Review Wild Fusion`s existing social media and blog content
        Identify posts with high engagement and low engagement
        Document insights and suggest potential improvements
     

Brief: 3
Scenario: Audience Research
 Tasks: 
        Use tools to analyze high net worth individuals as your target audience, their  demographics, interests, online behavior.
        Create 2-3 audience personas
        Suggest 10-15 content types that fit each persona


Brief: 4
Scenario: Social Media Strategy Drafting
 Tasks: 
        Draft a 1- month content calendar for Rexona with Teens and young adults as your target audience on Instagram and LinkedIn
        Include captions, hashtags, posting times, and media types
       

Brief: 5
      Scenario: Copywriting Practice
      Tasks: 
        Write a blog article for any brand of your choice
        Ensure tone aligns with brand voice
        Edit for clarity, engagement, and CTA effectiveness

